Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Prologue}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:17.03,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:47.03,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:34.11,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.08,0:22:30.12,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:00.09,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Epilogue}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.03,0:00:05.66,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,Don't try to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:11.36,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,He doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.98,0:00:17.58,Italics,,0,0,0,,think anything of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:21.83,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,So I'm not going to see him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.17,0:00:25.38,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,You're back, Nino{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:26.96,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:30.72,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I told you to stop calling me that.\NIt creeps me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:32.20,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, Nino.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:35.99,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,I just received word that \Nyou all passed the exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:39.01,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,The six of you managed to pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:40.52,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:42.27,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:45.86,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,It seems I have no choice but \Nto approve of Uesugi{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.86,0:00:47.60,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,So from tomorrow on,\Nhe can come here to...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.60,0:00:49.15,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I'm not going to see him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:53.49,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Also, we've decided to stay at \Nour new place for a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.81,0:00:54.90,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:57.87,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,We're not going to make Ichika \Ndo all the work, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:00:59.42,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I'm going to get a job, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:02.42,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I'm not going to pretend we've \Nbecome independent or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.42,0:01:04.41,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I know we're not doing \Nthe right thing, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:09.41,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,But I have a feeling that\Nliving like that will change us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.41,0:01:12.17,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I feel like we've made some progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.28,0:01:14.67,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,I fail to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.12,0:01:19.21,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,Abstract ideas like "progress"\Ncouldn't be less convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:23.04,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,I've seen your so-called new home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.59,0:01:26.06,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,To me, it looks like you've gone {\i1}backwards{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.49,0:01:29.06,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,You mustn't have forgotten \Nin just five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:32.82,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,You don't want to live \Nlike that anymore, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:35.11,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,Stop being selfish and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:38.07,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.21,0:01:46.19,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,There you are, Nino.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:47.71,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,We're going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:51.30,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Wh-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.30,0:01:52.21,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:55.09,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,We need to get back before work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:01:57.35,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,Nino.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:00.60,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,The path you're about to walk is a thorny one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.91,0:02:02.35,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,It won't end well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.86,0:02:05.48,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,You'll certainly going to regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:07.23,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:13.68,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Dad, just watch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:16.85,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:17.61,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:19.65,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:23.74,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'll be taking your daughter, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:26.62,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,Ebata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:30.91,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,It seems, happily, that my daughters\Nhave all passed the exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:33.68,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,Am I smiling like I should?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.48,Default,Ebata,0,0,0,,Of course, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.87,0:02:37.13,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:40.61,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,Of course I am. I am their father, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:44.76,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I thought I told you I was done with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.25,0:02:50.80,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,It seems that relationships \Nrequire mutual input, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:52.21,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.21,0:02:53.98,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,And where did you get this bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:55.82,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I borrowed it from my boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:03:00.86,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I told you, I used to do deliveries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:02.99,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,That's when I got my license.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:03.95,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.23,0:03:06.48,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You look shockingly tacky with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:09.33,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Aren't these your exam results?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:11.39,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,No! Don't look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:14.71,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I bet it turns out that you \Ngot 100 in all subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:18.55,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:21.20,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Biggest failure of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.59,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'm seriously embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:24.17,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Is this our fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.17,0:03:25.48,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,It isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:27.45,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Never mind that. I'm going to floor it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:28.56,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Hang on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:37.58,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,My long job as a tutor \Nhas come to a close today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:40.60,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Nino's right. I'm not needed anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:44.20,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,This is the end of our relationship, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:46.05,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'll miss it. Won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:51.14,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You're going so slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:52.65,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I thought you were going to floor it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:54.23,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What do you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:56.16,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'm carrying a lot of weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:59.37,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Huh? Who are you calling heavy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:01.58,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Jeez, you drive me crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:04.26,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You've always been like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:06.22,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,A jerk of the highest order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:09.14,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,And, also...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:12.98,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:53.24,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.37,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,You brought Nino back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:56.87,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,We're over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:58.00,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:00.27,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,I said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:01.50,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,I went said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:04.01,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,What's gotten into me? \NLiking someone like him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:06.63,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,That was my first confession!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:09.01,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,Why did I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:10.26,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:13.26,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,And why isn't he reacting at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.10,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:17.60,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Congratulations on making it\Nthrough the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:20.73,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I can't believe we pulled it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:21.69,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:24.65,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I want to frame our exam papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:28.03,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Why don't we do that when \Nget slightly better grades?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:32.03,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I know we're celebrating, \Nbut can we really afford all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:36.00,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,The owner is treating us to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.29,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,Remember to give us five stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:42.67,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Our orders are all over \Nthe place, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.96,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I guess this is business as usual for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.21,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Here, Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:46.80,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:48.17,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,What's this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:51.47,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Your predictions on the contemporary \Nliterature questions were spot on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:52.76,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,They were.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.06,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,That really helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:55.51,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Me too, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:56.35,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:57.26,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.14,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:04.94,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:09.49,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,You all helped me out, too, though.\NI have to return the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.45,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,We do, too, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:14.37,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Why don't we all share a little, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:17.83,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,That's how we made it\Nthrough the exams, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:21.08,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Plus, this way, we can enjoy \Nall the different flavors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:22.83,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,That's your real motivation, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.50,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Here, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:26.96,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:28.34,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,And congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:32.38,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I never would have thought \Nyou'd do the best, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:34.97,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I got lucky. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:38.73,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I'm beating you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:40.98,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:44.98,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,I'm going to take a short break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.61,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,You can handle it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:50.69,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Oh, boss, is it all right \Nif I set aside some pudding?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:52.49,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,Sure, but did you ever like pudding?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.49,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,No, it's in return for a Valentine's Day gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:58.45,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,I thought you were one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:00.62,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,Traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:02.16,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Uh, it was from my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:03.25,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:05.46,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,Oh, that's what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:08.76,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,I thought it was from one of the five girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:12.26,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,That would never happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:17.39,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Actually, I've been getting some \Nall the time since January.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:19.64,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Nah, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:21.43,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Working hard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.56,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Wh-Where's the boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:25.10,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,He just went into the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.02,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:28.86,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I was going to thank him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:30.53,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I guess I'll wait for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:35.78,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I hope I hid it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:40.83,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,It's true that I was rooting \Nfor Miku... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:43.54,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,But just for a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:47.79,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,Miku said she'd confess if she came in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:50.38,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,But I had the highest grade this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:54.30,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Does that mean I can?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:59.35,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Thanks for helping with the dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.22,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,It's in return for the treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:02.81,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You can go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.56,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'll let the boss know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:05.85,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Go have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:07.73,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:08.94,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.03,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:17.11,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Forget what I said on the bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:20.24,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I'm sure I troubled you with what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:22.15,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,It was so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:24.45,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I think I went too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:26.21,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:27.25,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Nino...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.09,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.67,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:38.59,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,It was so windy. I might have missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:41.72,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:42.35,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,No, I mean, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.14,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:46.35,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,I guess he never heard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:49.90,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,We aren't girlfriend material to him anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:53.52,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,He never even noticed when Miku gave \Nhim Valentine's Day chocolates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:57.41,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,I'm actually glad he didn't hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:10:00.20,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.74,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Boss, I'm done cleaning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:06.16,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I said I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:11.04,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:13.09,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I'm not asking for a response.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.30,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You're so frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:18.01,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,If you don't see me as girlfriend material,\NI'll {\i1}force{\i0} you to see me that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:21.14,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Remember how I said there's gotta be
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:24.72,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,at least one girl on this planet\Nwho'd fall for a guy like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:26.85,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,That girl is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:28.44,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Too bad for you!
Comment: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:36.69,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\b1\pos(948,594)\bord4.5\shad3\c&H0E0D0C&\3c&H131510&\4c&H0E0D0C&\frx6\fry344\frz6.71\t(22,256,1 \c&H66563D&\3c&HB3A38B&\4c&H66563D&)}Yamasoto
Comment: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:36.69,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\b1\pos(1470,540)\fs54\c&H080907&\3c&H202121&\t(22,256,1 \c&H483C35&\3c&HECF0F2&)\shad0\frx4\fry350\frz6.455}Open until {\c&H100D18&\t(22,256,1 \c&H5F459F&)}11 {\c&H080907&\t(22,256,1 \c&H483C35&)}PM
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:36.69,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,F-Futaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:37.78,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:39.20,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:40.53,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Are you shopping, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:42.41,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's my turn today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.82,0:10:45.53,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Weren't there some shops \Ncloser to your place? Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:50.37,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,It's not like I took a detour to come \Nto this shop in order to have a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,to run into you based on what I remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:56.42,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I was just walking when I naturally \Nfound myself at this shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:58.42,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,The longest tale in Miku history.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:10:59.76,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:00.43,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:01.80,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:02.55,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I came for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:04.14,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:05.76,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I never knew about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:07.47,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:09.02,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,This is the only place that does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:13.23,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,This hot spring is near \Nwhere our Grandpa lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:15.32,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You can't even trade hot \Nspring vouchers for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:18.15,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,The best prize is obviously \NPrize E, the gift coupons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:19.57,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:22.03,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,How much would Prize B fetch if you sold it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:24.45,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I have a feeling you would \Nnever win it, Futaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:26.70,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,We won't know until we try!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:27.79,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Let's go pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:28.70,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:30.75,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,There's something Nino wanted me to buy her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:33.59,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:36.13,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Has Nino said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.21,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:38.59,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,No, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.22,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:41.51,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Hey, Miku...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:44.72,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Is there anyone you have \Na crush on or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.72,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,There isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:50.43,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I already told you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:53.61,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,There isn't anyone in class that \Nyou've since developed feelings for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:55.98,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Let's talk about dating! Dating!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:58.11,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you, Futaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:00.03,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:04.28,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,An acquaintance of mine apparently\Ngot confessed to by a classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.03,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:08.49,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,They said they don't need \Na response, but, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:11.37,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Honestly, it's troubling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:15.38,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:18.38,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I didn't think you'd be one to \Nthink about that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:20.30,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,You're like a normal guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:22.13,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'm just asking for someone I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:26.10,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be the type \Nto dismiss that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:26.89,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.88,0:12:31.27,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,What happened to my acquaintance was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:37.23,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,She tried to confess, but she didn't \Nhave the guts to, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:41.03,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Once you do, you can't go back \Nto how things were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:44.19,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,So it takes a lot of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:46.82,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:47.53,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:51.16,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,I guess some people have that courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:54.41,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,I don't know how to face her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:57.29,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,Why am I such a coward?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:12:59.67,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Either way, it's spring break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:02.84,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,There's plenty of time to think.
Comment: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:03.55,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(389,1)\pos(960,786)\c&H7596B4&\3c&H1A2A57&\shad0}Gift campaign
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:06.76,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Spring break...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:11.81,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Whoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:15.77,Default,Fu's Dad,0,0,0,,Traveling is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:18.23,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,This is all thanks to Futaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.44,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.53,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,I can't believe I actually won.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:23.65,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:27.03,Default,Fu's Dad,0,0,0,,"The foremost tourist attraction \Nin the area: the Bell of Vows."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:32.79,Default,Fu's Dad,0,0,0,,It says, "Any man and woman who ring \Nthis bell together are forever bound."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:35.62,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Bro! Take a picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.41,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:40.21,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Shoot, I forgot to charge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:41.17,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.34,Default,Fu's Dad,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:43.63,Default,Fu's Dad,0,0,0,,Let's move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:45.22,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Come with us, {*}brother{*Onii-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:47.63,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:51.97,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'll forget about those girls \Nand enjoy this family vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:53.35,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:02.78,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-kun}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:03.73,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:04.65,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Why are {\i1}you{\i0} here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:06.86,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,You're so fast, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:08.20,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.74,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,It's Uesugi{**-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:10.95,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:14.33,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,You won, too, Futaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:16.50,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You guys are all here on \Na family vacation, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:17.69,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,This is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:20.06,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,Indeed, a family vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:22.88,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,But you must be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:26.17,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,You always have to expect something \Nto go wrong when you're traveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:28.97,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:30.89,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,Shall we have lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:33.06,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,Begin preparations, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:36.52,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,When did those girls work \Nthings out with their dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:38.27,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:39.69,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,N-Nino!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:40.65,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:43.02,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,If you have something to say, say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:44.40,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Futaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:47.19,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:49.28,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,The way you said his name, "Futaro"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.66,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nino?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:51.57,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:54.28,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,It's been half a year \Nsince we met each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:57.29,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,It's about time we get \Na bit closer, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.41,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.54,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I do agree with that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:02.08,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.66,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,How about nicknames?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:05.59,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Miku, think of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:06.30,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:07.59,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Ue...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:08.51,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Fu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:11.30,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Fu-ta{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:12.63,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Fu{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:13.68,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:15.68,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Hey, that's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:18.35,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Never mind that, let's get ready for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:20.23,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,All right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:21.31,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:24.07,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Yotsu—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:25.90,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I'm getting nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.32,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I don't know if I can do it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.81,0:15:32.70,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Ichika, could you explain something to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:36.70,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm in the middle \Nof something. Maybe later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:38.45,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.86,0:15:42.67,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,We've only been apart for a short while,\Nand they're all being distant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:45.17,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Itsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:48.16,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,Itsuki{**-kun}, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:50.92,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,Go retrieve our lunch boxes from Ebata.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:51.97,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:53.39,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:54.22,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,About the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:55.89,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,Now, then, let's prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:58.68,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,All of us are together for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.01,0:16:02.56,Default,Q's Dad,0,0,0,,I'm spending quality time \Nwith my family, privately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:06.23,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,See you, Futaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:07.94,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,We're probably at the same hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:09.32,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:12.32,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I need to speak with you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:18.83,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,It's like a haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:20.83,Default,Fu's Dad,0,0,0,,They're open, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:24.21,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,When is "later"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:25.71,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Maybe I should try calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:27.09,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:32.34,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,She was around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:37.10,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,When did she get up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:41.98,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Where did Itsuki go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:44.73,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:49.11,Default,Fu's Dad,0,0,0,,I'm in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:52.61,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Good thing there's a mixed bath. \NThe whole family can be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:55.86,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,You shouldn't stay in for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:16:57.24,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:01.25,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,She said she wanted to talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:02.75,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:11.63,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,This is Itsuki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:14.38,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Why is she being so roundabout?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:19.89,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Th-The courtyard is this way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.63,0:17:23.52,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Is he dead or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.59,0:17:26.40,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:28.61,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:30.86,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I was going to the courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:32.44,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:34.40,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,L-Let's just go to the courtyard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:35.07,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.11,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Tell me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.32,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:38.95,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:45.04,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,What is your understanding \Nof your relationship with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:45.82,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:47.62,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Well, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:51.09,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You said we're p-partners or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:54.76,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,No, we aren't partners anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:18:00.10,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,We aren't doing lessons very often \Nanymore, so I can't deny that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:02.97,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,But I've been hired to tutor \Nuntil you guys graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:05.23,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Until then, as your tutor, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:06.85,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,We're through with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.30,0:18:10.48,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Let's put an end to this relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:11.36,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:12.73,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:13.74,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Tell me what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:14.74,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:16.40,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Did your father tell you to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.24,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Why would you say that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:23.37,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:25.37,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I thought you were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:29.75,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Huh? Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:32.58,Default,Grandpa,0,0,0,,Don't you dare lay a hand \Non my granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:34.38,Default,Grandpa,0,0,0,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:38.09,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Screw this noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:39.55,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:43.97,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:45.14,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,It's morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:46.68,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:47.89,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:49.65,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Let me keep sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:52.86,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'm going to sleep forever \Nand fly off into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.15,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:55.40,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:57.78,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,{*}My brother is{*Onii-chan's} flying off into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:19:00.91,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Sorry to disappoint you, Itsuki{**-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:01.78,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:04.16,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Itsuki! What was that about yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:06.75,Italics,Itsuki,0,0,0,,That's what I'd like to ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:09.29,Italics,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Why didn't you come to the courtyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:12.13,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.42,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.30,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Let's meet up to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:21.30,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I would love to, but we're being watched\Ncarefully to make sure we don't see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:23.43,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I don't think I can get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:25.47,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,There's a good place, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:32.56,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Demiglace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:34.57,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,H-Hamburg steak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:38.53,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Okay, seems like you're \Nthe real Itsuki this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:45.37,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Yesterday, I met you at the front desk, \Nand I was told to stop tutoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:49.33,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,So that wasn't you, then, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:50.37,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,It wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:52.71,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,It could only have been one of my sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:54.96,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,It's settled, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:59.22,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,One of them is rejecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:01.63,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Did any of them seem suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:05.30,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Why did they disguise themselves as you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:07.10,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Oh, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:08.81,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:12.73,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,We seem to bump into each \Nother in the bath a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:13.81,Italics,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Nino?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:14.73,Italics,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:17.61,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Since we're here together...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:20.11,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Want me to wash you or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:22.70,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,H-Hang on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:23.87,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Let me ask you one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:24.91,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:27.49,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You aren't Itsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:28.66,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:29.99,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,No, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:32.37,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:42.21,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I worked up all my courage for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:44.39,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Screw him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:47.14,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,You were absolutely in the wrong there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.38,0:20:48.56,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,That's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:50.43,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You all look the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:20:54.10,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I don't think we're the same in every way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:56.90,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,We're able to tell ourselves \Napart, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:59.15,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I'm sure you could, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.28,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,All you need is love!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:02.40,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Here we go again with your crazy theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:04.95,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I'm baffled, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:07.28,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Nino used to hate you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:09.37,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,What could have changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:11.04,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,So that {\i0}was{\i1} Nino.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:13.29,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,It's not just Nino.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:16.08,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Ichika, Miku, Yotsuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.53,0:21:19.54,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,They've all been a bit weird\Nsince spring break started.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.91,0:21:23.93,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I called you out last night\Nto ask about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:26.18,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Can you think of a reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:30.85,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,I guess I wasn't just imagining things \Nwhen I noticed they've been acting odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.17,0:21:32.56,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:36.90,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Our top priority is solving \Nthe Fake Itsuki question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:39.69,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Unless we can figure out what \Nshe's really thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I may really be fired as your tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:43.74,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:48.82,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Though, there is something \NFake Itsuki said that I agree with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:52.62,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I don't know what she's after.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.40,0:21:56.71,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,But we aren't partners working \Ntoward the same goal anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:21:59.63,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Our many days spent studying \Nfor exams together,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,going to the fireworks festival, school camp, \Nlast year's end, and New Year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.70,0:22:07.59,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,We've shared so much time together now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.50,0:22:11.10,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you say we're friends at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:15.35,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.74,0:22:17.37,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,At the very most,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.37,0:22:19.10,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,we're complete strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:23.89,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You say that so unironically.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:26.36,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,My family vacation's ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:27.34,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Let's do this, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.87,0:22:29.39,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'll hear you guys out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.03,0:24:03.77,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,"Scrambled Eggs."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.77,0:24:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,

